snippet.textDisplay: I have a lot of long natural ashy blonde gray hair and I had purple color professionally applied to the bottom layer of hair in the back.  I can’t even imagine what it would have looked like it I’d tried it on my own.  People couldn’t tell  that my hair was dyed unless it was windy or my hair was in a bun.  I’ve been gray since my early 30s but now it is a popular color and I’m always getting compliments on the color.  I don’t like it though when strangers touch my hair.
